Package: cleandataframe
Type: Package
Title: Dataframe Cleaning and Conversion
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Harrison Zhu, Haifeng Zhu
Maintainer: <harrison0zhu@gmail.com>
Description: 
    Provides functions for cleaning and checking vectors and data frames in R.
    Has functionalities for checking and converting class type, encoding, formatting, and typos.
    Specifically allows for operating on duplicates and empty values within vectors.
    Added functionality for data frames and operating on duplicate or empty records and columns.
    Designed to make data processing much simpler and easy, cleaning up messy data
    before final touches are added on.
Imports:
    snakecase,
    stringdist
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests:
    rmarkdown,
    knitr
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
